      <%= image_tag 'quick.png' %>
      <p><h6>Quick and Easy</h6> Find the best meals from your favorite restaurants,<br>hotels or fresh groceries from supermarkets,<br> purchase them, pickup and enjoy at home.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="affordable">
      <%= image_tag 'affordable.png' %>
      <p><h6>Affordable</h6>Hundreds of surplus tasty meals and fresh groceries,<br>save up to 80% from restaurants,<br> hotels, and supermarkets prices.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="planet">
      <%= image_tag 'planet.png' %>
      <p><h6>Save the Planet</h6> Go green by caring about the environment,<br> reduce unnecessary emissions caused by food production.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

